your needs is to implement a Flower class which have seasons, 
I implemented a solution, is not the best, but it reveals the basic OOP inheritance mecanism and enums, ihope it will help you 

First, the season enum

```
 public enum Season{
        SUMMER, SPRING, WINTER, AUTUMN;

        public static List&lt;Season&gt; allSeason(){
            return Arrays.asList(values());
        }
    }
```
next the abstract class Flower

```
public abstract class Flower {
    abstract List&lt;Season&gt; seasons();
}
```
Then two classes that extends Flower and must define the seasons behaviour
```
class Poppy extends Flower{

    @Override
    List&lt;Season&gt; seasons() {
        return Arrays.asList(Season.SPRING, Season.SUMMER);
    }
}

class Anthurium extends Flower{

    @Override
    List&lt;Season&gt; seasons() {
        return Season.allSeason();
    }
}

```

